    Описание

    Сти́вен А́дам А́мелл — канадский актёр, наиболее известный по главной роли Оливера Куина в телесериале «Стрела» и Кейси Джонса в фильме «Черепашки-ниндзя 2». Википедия
    Дата и место рождения: 8 мая 1981 г. (возраст 44 года), Торонто, Канада
    Супруг или супруга: Кассандра Джин (в браке с 2012 г.), Каролин Лоуренс (в браке с 2007 г. до 2010 г.)
    Рост: 1,85 м
    Родители: Сандра Энн Болти, Томас Дж. Амелл

    Stephen Amell/Movies and shows
    Was Arrow a good series?
    ARROW is one of the best exponents of the new type of comic-book-derived drama, arguably as good as or even better than SMALLVILLE (which was, thematically, all over the map). Amell is great. He has a whispery kind of delivery which oddly makes what he says that much more interesting. The supporting cast is great.

    Are the Amell brothers or cousins?
    Early life and education. Robert Patrick Amell IV was born in April 1988 in Toronto, the son of Josephine "Jo" Burden and Robert Patrick "Rob" Amell III, who work in the custom jewelry business. His first cousin is Arrow actor, Stephen Amell.

    Is Stephen Amell in TVD?
    On December 3, 2010, Amell joined the cast of The Vampire Diaries as werewolf 'Brady' for season 2. Amell starred as the real life convicted killer Joran van der Sloot in the Lifetime film Justice for Natalee Holloway which originally aired in May 2011.
